{"tid":571574,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去咗今晚麥花臣場《份子引力》？","createTime":"2018-02-24T18:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T14:05:57.000Z","uid":89235,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3895fcf645de6409f331d4fc190f280a6fb4c7","tid":571574,"uid":89235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T18:38:13.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲打去咗？我覺得好正播！<br />\n之前只係聽開鄧小巧、黃靖同Nowhere Boys嘅歌<br />\n但show前聽吓per se，都幾啱自己口味，幾期待live<br />\n不過可能Stephen 把聲太柔，現場歌詞聽得唔係幾清楚，覺得咬字可以再改善吓<br />\n唱《天外飛仙》真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗佢地，都仲有黎曉陽、馮穎琪，仲有應該係監製為主嘅謝國維<br />\n今次估唔到得咁少觀眾，我知有部分人仲要係自己友/朋友，覺得都幾可惜，因為你地值得更多嘅聽眾㗎！<br />\n希望可以有多啲人留意佢地，如果你地睇到嘅話，好想同你地講，唔好灰心！！！會繼續支持你地㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/023811_5f2bc2a57c19cfb372fa2b63148b41c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F023811_5f2bc2a57c19cfb372fa2b63148b41c5.png&h=ab53bb90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"655c28edd9877317d0174a315e33d5fe1918f88a","tid":571574,"uid":89235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"傻㗎，咁都有腐皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪要利申非打手"},{"pid":"6886f528e3d538ec2936e2ac85dfd0fe0ff16029","tid":571574,"uid":106326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T19:01:41.000Z","msg":"淨係聽per se 其他不了"},{"pid":"a16f2e0859a1f5cd5a4aac0efaeb1cf1be29aa46","tid":571574,"uid":166833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"有去<br />\n真係意外地少人 目測好似得五成入座率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0d2dc78e0ba2597f56b97e167b6c2b505e8940","tid":571574,"uid":166833